				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3097810#post-3494479</guid>
				<title>Hey! Did I break the curse?</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3097810/scp-3666#post-3494479</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 22 Jul 2017 14:12:14 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>SpookyPizza</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2260541</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&quot;Desperation for a cure. When anarchy reigns and fear arises, authority ensues.&quot;</p> <p>Thanks for reading SCP-3666 and thanks to all these other wonderful people that read the article when it was a draft:</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Crit&nbsp;appreciation</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Close&nbsp;appreciation</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Overall, 17 people and more (I think) gave this feedback! Thanks to all of them.</p> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/noxfero" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3118085&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1502628809" alt="Noxfero" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3118085)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/noxfero" >Noxfero</a></span></p> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rigen" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2826105&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1502628809" alt="Rigen" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2826105)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rigen" >Rigen</a></span></p> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1502628809" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" >DrBleep</a></span></p> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/ava